summary: Makes Tamriel - the Beauty of Dawn - a vibrant, colorful world of fantasy.
descriptionHtml:
Tamriel is the name of The Elder Scrolls' world's major continent; named by the ancient Aldmer, it translates to "the Beauty of Dawn".

GPU: GTX970
RAM: 8gb

45FPS in populated exterior, 50 in empty exterior, 60 in interior.

Purity
Tamriel Reloaded HD

Please install various performance mods to smoothen your gaming experience. You can search these keywords to find which ones you need, each user has their own preference:
Performance, FPS, Remove, Optim


Originates from the ENBs "Skyrim Graphics Good" and RealVision, it is tweaked in my game to an extent where it can be a separate ENB of its own.
This ENB uses certain files (including DoF) from RealVision which are modified by myself in this ENB.

Installation guide:
1. Install the latest ENB binaries here: http://enbdev.com/download_mod_tesskyrim.html
2. Install this ENB's files
3. Overwrite everything
